node.text:
Where we start a haircut suggests where we want the control or which direction we want the length or weight to travel.
With short hair I feel if we start at the side the shape looks graduated and if we start from the back the shape looks more layered or flatter.
So when you look at a short haircut decide on its characteristics, does the shape look layered or graduated?
This decision will help you in deciding where to start the haircut.
